Place your files here:

  metadata.toml                   - Required. Edit with your show's info.
  banner.jpg                      - Optional. Any image file for the poster/banner.
  Episode Title_s1_ep1.mp4        - Video files following the naming convention.
  Episode Title_s1_ep2.mp4
  Episode Title_s1_ep3.mp4

Episode naming convention:
  <title>_s<season>_ep<episode>.<ext>

Examples:
  Pilot_s1_ep1.mp4
  The Journey Begins_s1_ep2.mp4
  New Horizons_s2_ep1.mp4

The part before _s becomes the episode title (underscores become spaces in the UI).
